   "source": [
    "# 🏢 AI-Powered Corporate Compliance & Regulations Assistant\n",
    "> **Author:** AI Engineer Ammar Nasir\n",
    "> **Tech Stack:** Python, LangChain, Chroma DB, Qwen-2.5-Instruct, PyTorch (CUDA), Gradio  \n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 📌 Project Introduction\n",
    "In modern enterprise environments, navigating extensive regulatory documents, compliance statutes, and operational frameworks introduces significant operational friction. Employees and auditing teams often spend valuable hours manually searching through hundreds of dense PDF pages, which slows down decision-making and increases the risk of compliance errors.\n",
    "\n",
    "To solve this problem, this project implements a **Production-Grade Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) Pipeline**. The system ingests raw corporate compliance documents, structurally parses them into layout-aware markdown nodes, and stores their high-dimensional vector representations in a persistent vector database (**Chroma DB**). By pairing this semantic index with a localized, GPU-accelerated Large Language Model (**Qwen-2.5-1.5B-Instruct**), the application delivers a secure, conversational corporate portal. It enables employees to fetch verified, context-constrained, and completely hallucination-free policy answers in real time."
   ]
  },
